dc_title_s: C-38 Geologic Atlas of Kanabec County, Minnesota
dc_description_s: Surface and bedrock geology of Kanabec County, Mn., also includes data-base information, bedrock topography, depth to bedrock in GIS and image formats, as well subsurface interpretations of sand distribution between the land and bedrock surfaces.; The U.S. Geological Survey as part of the 2013 State Geologic Mapping Program Element (Statemap) of the National Cooperative Geologic Mapping Program, The Kanabec County Board of Commissioners, and the Minnesota Legacy Amendment's Clean Water Fund
dct_isPartOf_sm: Minnesota Geological Survey County Atlas Series
